Posts.Content: Donna, I too got a callback today. I missed the call so I will have to call tomorrow to schedule the appt. I'm guessing that they won't be able to tell me much. I am 36 and this was my very first mammogram. I think that my breasts are dense and I'm wondering if that could be the reason. I hate worrying but I always do. I'm sorry that you don't have support! I am praying for both of us that it's nothing.
Posts.Title: Second Call back On Mammogram and scared

Posts.Content: Ok, I am going back today and they said that they are going to be doing another mammogram and an ultrasound because my right breast is dense.  I'm guessing that this is so that they can get a good baseline.  I'll post again when I hear more.
